      <section name='elevator'>

         <para number='1' comment='Elevator from loc 530 down'>
         With a clanking noise, the doors close and the elevator jerks into motion. The descent is not very smooth, and when it reaches the lower level it stops with a severe jerk. Clearly the Selena authorities don't believe in spending money maintaining facilities that are only used by staff.
         </para>

         <para number='2'>
         The doors rattle open and you step out.
         </para>

         <para number='3' comment='Elevator up from 600'>
         There is a screech of tormented metal and the doors slam shut. The elevator machinery gives a groan, the gearing graunches, and it slowly heaves itself upwards to the next level.
         </para>

         <para number='4'>
         The doors open and you walk out.
         </para>

      </section>

